Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊 正治 天氣很好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 至少星期天讓我好好睡睡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不出去太浪費了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.80,0:01:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.60,0:01:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 呆在屋裡也無聊的很
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.40,0:01:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算放鬆一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.40,0:01:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在晴朗的週末裡兩人一起出門玩真是太開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下 怎麼能算是兩個人一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此 我也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.80,0:02:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是 你隨便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.80,0:02:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.10,0:02:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.00,0:02:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥 帶著我逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.80,0:02:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶！ 怎麼了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊的愛情大作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來全家人要一起出門
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.80,0:02:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊看上去不太願意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 他們還是新婚夫婦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得的休息日 我希望他們不受別人打擾的度過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊 原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之小刊就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸真是的 竟然把女兒拜託給別人了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.80,0:03:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本說的就不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.50,0:03:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽很期待…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要掛念著我的事 你們走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸拜託你好好照顧我的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和正治兩人的好時光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.10,0:03:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的 又被班裡的男生告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在都已經是第六次了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我同齡的男生我可是一點興趣也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是這樣嗎 真是辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.30,0:04:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是大哥哥的話隨時都可以做你的女朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好 那真是多謝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.90,0:04:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又把我當小孩子來看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 難得全家人能一起出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣真的好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總感到累呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那個人那麼的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 跟爸爸再婚的人不論再怎麼努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的媽媽只有在天國的那一個而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要粘著我哦 這樣不好走路了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:05:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 在人群裡迷路太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是約會的話 這樣也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.10,0:05:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.60,0:05:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩是之前遇到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤… 澤村居然跟那麼小的孩子約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣 比起過了二十歲的阿姨們我一直都更迷人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 從小孩子起就開始交往總算值了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會變成這樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋笨蛋 那種事怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 一起拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.90,0:05:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍大頭貼 還粘得那麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也不能裝作沒看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九萬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.80,0:06:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純正九連寶燈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,役滿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九萬六千點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 大哥哥 下面玩這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我挑激鬥 你還真是有膽量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.05,0:06:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會輸的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格鬥就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.60,0:06:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:57.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！ 格鬥遊戲對戰不敗的我居然會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.80,0:07:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.20,0:07:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 哪個按鍵是幹什麼的都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.40,0:07:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我來指示
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按我說的鍵去摁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.50,0:07:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好嗎 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這次可不會放水了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 A鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.30,0:07:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就這樣摁著再摁C鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣突入所有的鍵連擊連擊連擊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AADDC…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.40,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來 快起來喲 嵐君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利我收下了呢 交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.20,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 要被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.20,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝者 嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥 太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你對我的男朋友都幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙再怎麼不受歡迎也不能對小學生出手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笨蛋啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.20,0:08:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.70,0:08:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰居家孩子的臨時保姆啊 好像潑你冷水了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐才是為什麼一個人到處晃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想偶爾回家看看的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在自己喜歡的時候才回家真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.50,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也沒說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.10,0:09:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來難得的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.00,0:09:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡正治吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算隱藏起來我也知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能兩個人獨處　而在生悶氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要嘗試下不倫戀情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 與你無關吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真的話幫你一下也是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.70,0:09:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓對正治所有事都瞭然於胸的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這凜大姐當你的特別教練吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊受你照顧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 請不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是不會對你寶貴的大小姐幹什麼壞事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.30,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個熱心腸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要講這種奇怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.50,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 教練？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.50,0:10:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老姐 又在搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.90,0:10:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼回家吧 小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 快點走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.10,0:11:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接續詞as的用法是很複雜的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在有as的地方 從全文來看 弄清楚是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.80,0:11:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看第一個例子 as you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管正治的睡相再怎麼可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用這麼盯著看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤… 澤村
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 澤村同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤村？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.80,0:12:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你這傢伙在幹什麼!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.10,0:12:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要向大哥哥請教作業
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作業？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學生程度的作業應該還能應付的來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 首先扮成迎接丈夫歸來的年輕妻子已經成功
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜大姐策劃 愛情魔法大作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.80,0:12:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始敬請期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 我不懂這個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 怎樣 我帶著眼鏡的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一定能夠俘獲大哥哥的心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.80,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 原來你眼睛不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.00,0:12:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行呀 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.20,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 原來他不是為眼鏡女而興奮的類型呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.20,0:13:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 進行下一步作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.10,0:13:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上嘍 小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 教練
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 怎樣 我穿制服的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 那不是老姐的制服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便穿的話會沒命的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕 一定要趕緊脫下來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效果 嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣穿的話感冒了怎麼辦 快穿上這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.10,0:13:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 沒想到是這麼棘手的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.80,0:13:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 現在可不是意氣消沉的時候哦 小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.70,0:13:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣的話 可要來點殺手鑭了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了 老公教我功課瞄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊咄 教我功課呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快教我功課 哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.70,0:14:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想學習的話給我早點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.90,0:14:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這些難道都是姊姊搞出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.20,0:14:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.50,0:14:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了你還有誰會教孩子幹這種亂七八糟的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 現在很消沉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在懷疑自己作為女孩有沒有魅力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魅力？ 不是還是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是孩子 但也是女孩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那份纖細的少女情懷 不注意是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去 你沒什麼資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.60,0:14:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡水好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 混蛋大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.60,0:14:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是姊姊令人意外的有幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.30,0:14:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是擔心著小刊的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你太幼稚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人可是以陷害別人為樂的魔鬼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果輕信的話到死都只是她的玩偶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 都唆使孩子幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約好了讓你們在浴室相見的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.10,0:15:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢隨便玩弄別人感情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑也要有限度呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可原諒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小子很有意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要輕舉妄動的話可不要後悔喲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.30,0:15:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人都不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.60,0:15:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊姊只是為我考慮才幫我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.70,0:15:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我最喜歡大哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是大哥哥只是把我當成小孩子對待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.70,0:16:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這樣的小女孩不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.50,0:16:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事哦 小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙更小的也喜歡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.00,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 小刊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那樣頑固的傢伙現在是交不到女朋友的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 這也是那傢伙的優點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔鬼 惡魔 乳牛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.30,0:16:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說了是夢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在浴室時摔倒暈了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 果然是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看嘛 我一直都是受傷纏著繃帶的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說在我右手上看到女孩子果然是奇怪的夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:17:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我好想成為大哥哥的右手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話就能夠一直呆在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 已經過了八點了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊 該回家了 很晚了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回不了家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.00,0:17:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很晚了 媽媽很擔心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天做了小刊最喜歡吃的漢堡包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 回去一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.40,0:17:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.60,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想回那樣的家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這兒和大哥哥一起過
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.20,0:17:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎 大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.10,0:17:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 你在說什麼話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.10,0:17:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.10,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉強自己扮成媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.10,0:18:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你多麼努力我的媽媽只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:06.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實只想和爸爸兩個人一起生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在對你比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你是成為不了我的媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼不能瞭解我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想… 和你好好相處而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也應該瞭解了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽是真心掛念著你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:41.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了就快點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.30,0:18:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別固執了 坦白一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天國裡的媽媽一定也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我才沒有固執呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是擔心大哥哥會在我回去後太寂寞而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 怎麼可能會寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了 好想吃漢堡包呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.30,0:19:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小刊看呀 好漂亮的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.70,0:19:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 大哥哥借你耳朵說句話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留個印記你就不會寂寞了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.20,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨… 笨蛋 快點走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人關係變得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白一點嗎？ 我很感動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不這麼講那傢伙看起來是不肯回去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 凌瀨？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 走的有點急 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊對了 這個你也可以的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.70,0:20:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞到了兩張電影票 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好一起去看的女孩子突然來不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是 扔掉不也是太浪費了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 這樣的話想送給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正治 這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個很想去看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 不想去得話沒必要這樣說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去我去 一定要去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.80,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那麼明天一點星側車站前見呢
